extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Search for a Book, Author, Genre or a Book Instance

  form(action="/catalog/search" method="GET")
    div.form-group
      label(for='search_bar') Search:
      input#search_bar.form-control(type="text" name="search_bar")
    button.btn.btn-primary(type="submit") SEARCH

  h1 Dynamic content

  p The library has the follwing record counts:

  ul
    li #[strong Books:] !{book_count}
    li #[strong Copies:] !{book_instance_count}
    li #[strong Copies available:] !{book_instance_available_count}
    li #[strong Author:] !{author_count}
    li #[strong Genres:] !{genre_count}

